updates.HtmlString: Added tokens which were missing. Updated marketing cards to be more accurate for set, plus set chances as 1:3 token:marketing for core sets, 2:3 for expansions, and 9:1 as of Battle for Zendikar.
Taplands are now replace basic lands in 5/12 packs.
No longer includes Nexus of Fate (promo) or promo land in boosters. Added promos.
